@MarkovApp.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5264

### Calculate Regular Markov Chain
POST {{MarkovApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/markov/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "transitionMatrix": [
    [0.7, 0.3],
    [0.4, 0.6]
  ],
  "initialStateVector": [0.5, 0.5],
  "isAbsorbing": false,
  "maxIterations": 1000
}

### Calculate Absorbing Markov Chain
POST {{MarkovApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/markov/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "transitionMatrix": [
    [1.0, 0.0, 0.0],
    [0.5, 0.0, 0.5],
    [0.0, 0.0, 1.0]
  ],
  "initialStateVector": [0.0, 1.0, 0.0],
  "isAbsorbing": true
}

###
